scene.message:
Ms. Saeko: SEBEC, huh...{wait_fr:32}{nl}
Those guys...!{wait_fr:21}{nl}
Sorry {ctl0f:1}, but{nl}
could you help?{waitkey}Go to the wall breach and{nl}
tell Yukino to stop{nl}
patching it.{waitkey}Inaba and Nanjo might{nl}
be coming back{nl}
that way.{waitkey}{ret}

Maki's mother: I am so{nl}
sorry for all the{nl}
trouble I've caused...{waitkey}{ret}

Ms. Saeko: They know about{nl}
the wall breach, right?{waitkey}Since the gate is locked,{nl}
that's the only way{nl}
to get in.{waitkey}{ret}

Agastya Tree: Young one...{nl}
Well met, that you have{nl}
come to me.{waitkey}{ret}

Agastya Tree:{nl}
Shall I engrave your{nl}
record within me?{waitkey}{nl}
{ctl0e:0}{ret}

Agastya Tree: Young one...{nl}
Take care as{nl}
you journey on.{waitkey}{ret}

Natsumi: Sonoda's mother's{nl}
injury isn't too bad.{nl}
You needn't worry.{waitkey}{clearbox}And you, {ctl0f:1}?{nl}
Are you hurt?{nl}
Let me check.{waitkey}{ret}
